Function reference

All functions

admin_download_proposals()
Download project proposals from Google Form.
admin_gh_add_contributor_to_repo()
Add a contributor to a repo.
admin_gh_add_user_to_team()
Add the user to the SDCA GitHub Organization UK Biobank team.
admin_gh_list_repos()
List all the repos on GitHub under the SDCA UK Biobank project.
admin_list_approved_projects()
List the approved projects connected to the UK Biobank at SDCA.
admin_start_approved_project()
Start and setup the approved project onto GitHub.
builder_table_exporter()
Build, but not run, the dx table exporter command.
create_csv_from_database()
Extract variables you want from the UKB database and create a CSV file to later upload to your own project.
download_data()
Downloads your UKB data file to the data/data.csv folder.
get_proj_dependencies()
Get package dependencies from the DESCRIPTION file.
get_rap_project_id()
Get the RAP project ID, will be the project main folder.
get_username()
Get the username of the user's who started the RStudio session.
project_variables
All variables found within the UK Biobank
rap_variables
Variable names that are specific to the RAP
read_parquet()
Read a Parquet file and convert to DuckDB format.
setup_git_config()
Add your name and email to Git's config settings.
setup_ukb_project()
Setup the project structure for working within the RAP.
setup_ukb_rap()
Run standard setup tasks in the UKB RAP after opening it up.
statements
Textual statements required by UK Biobank.
subset_rap_variables()
Take the selected UKB variables from the protocol stage and subset the RAP specific variables list.
upload_data()
Upload a data file to the RAP.
